	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />a word of caution: just because patents expire doesnt mean they arent still protected.
<br />
<br />one of the biggest things you have to watch when making your own carts is the bevel on the underside of the NES cart. you cant just make a bevel like on nintendo's carts.... you either have to make the cartridge thinner with curved corners so that it will move up into the connector above the bevels.... or just use a 90 degree angle in place of the bevels.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


